  Translator: Burton Watson
By: Zhuangzi
Locus:
  Chapter: 5
  Paragraph: 10
Title: The Sign Of Virtue Complete
---
Shen-t'u Chia, who had lost a foot, was studying under Pohun Wu-jen
along with Tzu-ch'an of Cheng. Tzu-ch'an said to Shen-t'u Chia, "If I
go out first, you stay behind, and if you go out first, I'll stay
behind."
